# Apex is the marketing landing. Any legacy app path hit here (old bookmarks,
# already-shared profile links, crawler caches) forwards to the app subdomain.
# Cloudflare Pages preserves the query string (e.g. ?u=username) automatically.
/profile/*   https://app.sarawaktalents.com/profile/:splat   301
/profile     https://app.sarawaktalents.com/profile          301
/join/*      https://app.sarawaktalents.com/join/:splat       301
/join        https://app.sarawaktalents.com/join              301
/admin/*     https://app.sarawaktalents.com/admin/:splat      301
/admin       https://app.sarawaktalents.com/admin             301
